experience.title: Sales Associate
experience.description: Greeted customers; described merchandise; helped locate items; computed sales prices; processed payments; answered questions; prepared sales slips; displayed merchandise; monitored security; inventoried stock; handled exchanges and returns.

experience.title: Cashier/Crew Leader
experience.description: Received payments by cash, check, or card; issued receipts; assisted customers; greeted and advised customers; supervised others; maintained inventories; performed some food preparation or service tasks when needed; tracked sales and item profitability.

experience.title: Crew Member
experience.description: Performed cleaning duties: serviced or supplied restrooms; emptied trash; cleaned floors; prepared cleaning solutions; notified managers of repairs; cleaned windows and laboratory equipment; dusted and polished furniture; maintained cleanliness of facilities.

experience.title: Shoe Dept Lead Supervisor
experience.description: Enforced safety and sanitation regulations; directed and coordinated activities of staff; planned schedules and production sequences; inspected materials and equipment; conducted training; analyzed production data; determined standards and budgets; motivated employees; managed personnel actions; planned new products and processes.
